6. ESP LOGIC

---

MODE 1: WRITE MODE


* Request UUID from backend
* Wait for RFID card
* Write UUID to card
* Notify backend

MODE 2: READ MODE

* Wait for RFID card
* Read UUID
* Send UUID to backend
* Receive tourist info

